    <h2>BWH - Standard WebSite Hosting</h2>
    <h3>Wish to have a personal or Business WebSite hosted?</h3>
    <p>
    We laughingly call this &#8220;The Standard Hosting&#8221; Solution. Amusing because it is far from &#8220;basic&#8221; or any other thoughts that spring to mind regarding a &#8220;standard&#8221; service. All our hosted Sites come with a broad range of available modules allowing any client to manage their Site as they see fit. Your Site can grow, if, and when, you decide to add more content or different areas. You may however only want a limited Solution to meet your needs. This could include, only as a very rough guideline, the following:
    </p>
    <div class='halfL bgGrey'>
      <b>Personal Hosted WebSite Example:</b>
      <ul>
      <li class='uc'>
        A HomePage 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( A starting 'jump-in' point for any site )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        An &#8220;About Me&#8221; Page 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Basics about who you are )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Contact Details Page 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Where you are and how to contact you )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Hobbies &amp; Interests Pages 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Further information 'about you' )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Photo Galleries 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Share your pictures with the world )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Private / Shared - Blogs 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Have your say with a weblog )</span>
      </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class='halfR bgGrey'>
      <b>Business Hosted WebSite Example:</b>
      <ul>
      <li class='uc'>
        A HomePage 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( A starting 'jump-in' point for any site )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Overview of Products / Services 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( What you have to offer )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Contact Details Page 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Where you are and how to contact you )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Detailed Products / Services Pages 
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( More info about your business &amp; products )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Products / Services Galleries
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Showcase your products and / or services )</span>
      </li><li class='uc'>
        Company Updates / News Page
        <br /><span class='smTxt'>( Up to date news about your business )</span>
      </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <br class='brB' />
    <p>
    You get the idea... We mention this as we are aware not everyone wishes to have or maintain an all &#8220;bells and whistles&#8221; concern. Our Standard Hosting Solution will cater for a personal Site with only a handful of pages to be easily created, updated and managed, or also allow a Company or other business venture a presence on the Internet that need not be huge or overly dynamic.
    </p><p>
    All sites, regardless of nature are Database driven which enables us to provide you with the <a href='cms_indx.html' title='CMS Hosting Details'>Content Management System</a> - <acronym title='Content Management System'>CMS</acronym>, which controls your Site. This is a very powerful tool and explains, in part, why our so called &#8220;Standard Hosting&#8221; package is not so standard...
    </p>
